### Step 2 — Package sl_agent into crispro-backend-v2 (Day 1-2)

**Decision**: Direct copy. Git submodule adds complexity. pip-installable git dependency adds fragility.

**Recommendation**: Copy `sl_agent/` directly into crispro-backend-v2 and track it in the main repo going forward. The `Synthetic-Lethality` silo repo becomes the origin reference.

